    <item>
      <title>What is Sin?</title>
      <link>/wiaposts/What-is-Sin/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 08:33:00 +0530</pubDate>
      <author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author>
      <guid>/wiaposts/What-is-Sin/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;
    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;/assets/images/wiapost/5255-What-is-Sin.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;What-is-Sin&#34; /&gt;
      
    &lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;What Is Sin? 
    &lt;div id=&#34;what-is-sin&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34;
            style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#what-is-sin&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You lose a loved one, a bond, or your health,&lt;br&gt;
Blame it on God, Fate, or Karma’s stealth.&lt;br&gt;
You feel consoled, the burden shared,&lt;br&gt;
But deep within, you&amp;rsquo;re still ensnared.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You blame the system, the people, the ways,&lt;br&gt;
And disgust fills the remaining days.&lt;br&gt;
But no matter where the blame is cast,&lt;br&gt;
The suffering lingers, it seems to last.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Cause Of Pain And Suffering</title>
      <link>/wiaposts/cause-of-pain-and-suffering/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author>
      <guid>/wiaposts/cause-of-pain-and-suffering/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;
    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;/assets/images/wiapost/5124-Cause-Of-Pain-And-Suffering.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Cause Of Pain And Suffering&#34; /&gt;
      
    &lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Cause Of Pain And Suffering 
    &lt;div id=&#34;cause-of-pain-and-suffering&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34;
            style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#cause-of-pain-and-suffering&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I am a body.  &lt;br&gt;
Therefore I must have pain and comfort.  &lt;br&gt;
And I can cause pain and comfort for others.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I am a mind.  &lt;br&gt;
Therefore I feel love and hate for others.  &lt;br&gt;
Hence I feel enjoyment and suffering.  &lt;br&gt;
And as a mind, I can cause enjoyment and suffering for others.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
